       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. CLOSPEN2.
      * CLOSURE PENALTY - SITE-CONFIGURABLE DAY BASIS (SEE WSDAYBAS)
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       COPY WSDAYBAS.
       01  WS-INPUTS.
           05  WS-ELAPSED-DAYS       PIC 9(4) VALUE ZERO.
           05  WS-WEEKEND-DAYS       PIC 9(4) VALUE ZERO.
       01  WS-WORK-AREAS.
           05  WS-CHARGE-DAYS        PIC S9(5) VALUE ZERO.
           05  WS-PENALTY-AMT        PIC 9(7)V99 VALUE ZERO.
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       1000-MAIN.
           ACCEPT WS-ELAPSED-DAYS
           ACCEPT WS-WEEKEND-DAYS
           PERFORM 2000-CALC
           DISPLAY 'PENALTY: ' WS-PENALTY-AMT
           STOP RUN.
       2000-CALC.
           IF BASIS-WORKING
              COMPUTE WS-CHARGE-DAYS = WS-ELAPSED-DAYS
                      - WS-WEEKEND-DAYS - 7
           ELSE
              COMPUTE WS-CHARGE-DAYS = WS-ELAPSED-DAYS - 7
           END-IF
           IF WS-CHARGE-DAYS > ZERO
              COMPUTE WS-PENALTY-AMT = WS-PEN-RATE-STD * WS-CHARGE-DAYS
           ELSE
              MOVE ZERO TO WS-PENALTY-AMT
           END-IF.
